# 🧠 Today's Core Understanding

### Pointer

* Stores address
* Can change target
* Can be null

### Reference

* Alias
* Cannot be null
* Cannot change target

### Memory Layout

#### Code Segment

Program instructions

#### Data Segment

Global/static variables

#### Stack

Local variables

#### Heap

Dynamic memory

